《'''湯姆在農莊'''》（{{lang-fr|'''''Tom à la ferme'''''}}，{{lang-en|'''''Tom at the Farm'''''}}）是一部2013年的加拿大心理驚悚片，由[[札維耶·多藍|札維耶·多藍]]執導。電影改編自{{link-en|米歇爾·馬克·伯查德|Michel Marc Bouchard}}的同名戲劇。於2013年9月2日本片參與了[[第70屆威尼斯影展|第70屆威尼斯影展]]的正式競賽<ref name="Venice">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia70 |title=Venezia 70 |accessdate=2013-07-27 |work=labiennale |archive-date=2013-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728070816/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia70 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Guardian">{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/25/venice-film-festival-2013-line-up/ |title=Venice film festival 2013: the full line-up |accessdate=2013-07-27 |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=25 July 2013 |archive-date=2013-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725191906/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/25/venice-film-festival-2013-line-up |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/screenings/sept2.html | title=2 September | work={{noitalic|www.labiennale.org}} | publisher=[[Venice_Film_Festival|Venice Film Festival]] | accessdate=2013-08-16 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016043313/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/70th-festival/screenings/sept2.html | archivedate=2015-10-16 }}</ref>，並在{{link-en|2013年多倫多國際電影節|2013 Toronto International Film Festival}}的特別介紹中入列<ref name="TIFF">{{cite web |url=http://tiff.net/filmsandschedules/festival/2013/tomatthefarm |title=Tom at the Farm |accessdate=2013-08-07 |work=TIFF |archive-date=2013-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130816022024/http://tiff.net/filmsandschedules/festival/2013/tomatthefarm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該片在威尼斯獲得了[[國際影評人協會|國際影評人協會獎]]<ref name="FIPRESCI">{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/awards-and-festivals/tiff/quebec-director-xavier-dolan-takes-prize-in-venice-film-to-screen-at-tiff/article14176457/ |title=Quebec director Xavier Dolan takes prize in Venice, film to screen at TIFF |accessdate=2013-09-07 |work=Globe and Mail |location=Toronto |date=7 September 2013 |archive-date=2015-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627170747/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/awards-and-festivals/tiff/quebec-director-xavier-dolan-takes-prize-in-venice-film-to-screen-at-tiff/article14176457/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影於2013年9月2日在威尼斯上映、2014年3月28日在加拿大、2014年4月16日在法國，而台灣則於2014年7月18日發布。

本片入圍{{link-en|第二屆加拿大電影獎|2nd Canadian Screen Awards}}的[[最佳電影|最佳電影]]提名<ref name=nominations>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/canadian-screen-awards-orphan-black-less-than-kind-enemy-nominated-1.2494447 "Canadian Screen Awards: Orphan Black, Less Than Kind, Enemy nominated"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/canadian-screen-awards-orphan-black-less-than-kind-enemy-nominated-1.2494447 |date=20180331112921 }}. [[CBC_News|CBC News]], January 13, 2014.</ref>。

== 劇情 ==
在廣告公司工作的湯姆是個同性戀，他參與了男朋友吉翁的喪禮，但在場的人卻沒有人認識他（因為眾人並不知他與吉翁的私密關係），吉翁的農夫哥哥法蘭西不太喜歡他，並要求要湯姆在死者母親的面前上演一場扭曲的遊戲、用謊言來別讓伯母傷心；湯姆和法蘭西兩人意見並不太合，在這封閉思想的農莊，湯姆逐漸陷入了難解的家庭糾紛中...。

