== 評價 ==
《湯姆在農莊》在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上根據28條點評獲得了79％的新鮮度，平均得分7.1／10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tom_a_la_ferme_2013/ |title=Tom at the Farm |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |date= |accessdate=5 April 2014 |archive-date=2014-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814220104/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tom_a_la_ferme_2013/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基於7條點評得分71<ref>{{cite web | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/tom-at-the-farm | title=''Tom at the Farm'' | accessdate=TBA | archive-date=2014-06-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140601211838/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/tom-at-the-farm | dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[imdb|imdb]]上則得分7.0<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2427892/ |title=Tom at the Farm |publisher=[[imdb|imdb]] |date=16 April 2014 |accessdate=2014-08-14 |archive-date=2014-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725100720/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2427892/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，電影獲得普遍好評。《[[衛報|衛報]]》的{{link-en|彼得·布拉德肖|Peter Bradshaw}}形容電影為「用熱情和恐懼所盤繞的有趣[電影]」<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/apr/03/tom-at-the-farm-review|title = Tom at the Farm (Tom à la Ferme) review|date = April 3, 2014|accessdate = April 5, 2014|website = The Guardian|first = Peter|last = Bradshaw|archive-date = 2014-10-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141014223729/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/apr/03/tom-at-the-farm-review|dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[RealNetworks|Film.com]]的大衛·艾利希則給了電影7.7的評級<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.film.com/movies/tom-at-the-farm-review|title = TIFF Review: ‘Tom at the Farm’|date = September 7, 2013|accessdate = March 13, 2014|website = Film.com|last = Ehrlich|first = David|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131016012758/http://www.film.com/movies/tom-at-the-farm-review|archivedate = 2013年10月16日}}</ref>。《[[愛爾蘭時報|愛爾蘭時報]]》的塔拉·布雷迪給了它5五顆星，並稱讚其為「天才之作」<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.irishtimes.com/culture/film/tom-at-the-farm-tom-%C3%A0-la-ferme-1.1748944|title = Tom at the Farm/Tom à la Ferme|date = April 4, 2014|accessdate = April 5, 2014|website = Irish Times|first = Tara|last = Brady|archive-date = 2014-07-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140705095627/http://www.irishtimes.com/culture/film/tom-at-the-farm-tom-%C3%A0-la-ferme-1.1748944|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

